column1: Protein count, spectral count, and NSAF Raw Data of Ixodes scapularis saliva proteins
Saliva was collected from ticks that fed on rabbits for  24, 48, 72, 96, and 120 h, ticks that were engorged but not detached (BD) and ticks that were engorged and detached (SD)
Column A provides the accession number for each protein from NCBI database.
Column B - BL provides the Peptide Count, Spectral Count, and NSAF values in tandem for each indiviudal run per time point
A value of (-1) represents that peptides were not detected.
A positive values represents that peptides were detected.
